<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:08:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>舒默参议员：不要邀请内塔尼亚胡。他不是你的盟友或朋友。他从来都不是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</link><description>向以色列坚定的民主党盟友传达的信息：不要邀请本杰明·内塔尼亚胡参加国会。他的唯一目的是在执行特朗普的命令时破坏美国总统乔·拜登的连任竞选</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 15:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</guid></item><item><title>1956 年以色列巴勒斯坦村庄发生的大屠杀被搬上银幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/the-1956-massacre-that-haunts-a-palestinian-village-in-israel-makes-it-to-the-screen/0000018f-ab36-d24f-a5df-fff6e5170000</link><description>同样在本周的文化综述中：一位艺术家讲述了她的父母被绑架到加沙的故事，获得了大奖； 《加沙之美》在戛纳备受争议；穆斯拉拉混合唤醒了耶路撒冷；穆罕默德·阿博·萨尔姆 (Muhammad Abo Salme) 为特拉维夫带来一线光明</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 15:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/the-1956-massacre-that-haunts-a-palestinian-village-in-israel-makes-it-to-the-screen/0000018f-ab36-d24f-a5df-fff6e5170000</guid></item><item><title>“这只是一次公关活动”：爱尔兰总统驳斥了爱尔兰反犹太主义的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/simply-a-pr-exercise-irish-president-belittles-claims-of-antisemitism-in-ireland/0000018f-b511-d24f-a5df-fff766580000</link><description>以色列驻爱尔兰大使发表了有关打击爱尔兰反犹太主义的声明，希金斯总统立即谴责该声明“不负责任”。 “爱尔兰人并不反犹太主义，”他辩称，并接着提到前任总统说希伯来语</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/simply-a-pr-exercise-irish-president-belittles-claims-of-antisemitism-in-ireland/0000018f-b511-d24f-a5df-fff766580000</guid></item><item><title>停止！现在！我们以色列士兵的母亲要求结束加沙徒劳的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/stop-now-we-mothers-of-israeli-soldiers-demand-an-end-to-the-futile-war-in-gaza/0000018f-b3c9-d390-ab8f-f3c9fa920000</link><description>我是以色列国防军士兵家长运动的一部分，他们曾经支持这场战争，但现在反对这场战争，这场战争已成为我们孩子毫无意义的死亡陷阱，一场由不愿结束的极端主义政府领导的战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/stop-now-we-mothers-of-israeli-soldiers-demand-an-end-to-the-futile-war-in-gaza/0000018f-b3c9-d390-ab8f-f3c9fa920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军警调查预备役军人呼吁加沙大规模反抗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-police-investigating-reservist-calling-for-mass-insubordination-in-gaza/0000018f-b466-d24f-a5df-fee668820000</link><description>警方确认视频中的嫌疑人是来自荷兹利亚的预备役军人，并表示他们已将他带去接受审问。该视频在社交媒体上广泛传播，总理的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡也被广泛转发，视频声称 10 万名以色列国防军预备役军人不服从离开加沙的命令</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-police-investigating-reservist-calling-for-mass-insubordination-in-gaza/0000018f-b466-d24f-a5df-fee668820000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日最后一刻的战斗从哈马斯手中拯救了 12 条生命</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-last-minute-october-7-battle-that-saved-the-lives-of-12-thai-workers/0000018f-a973-df13-a3af-bd77230c0000</link><description>10月7日，哈马斯恐怖分子在梅法西姆基布兹抓获12名泰国工人后，他们的上司到处寻找他们。他们最终被以色列安全部队救出，然后被绑架到加沙</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 13:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-last-minute-october-7-battle-that-saved-the-lives-of-12-thai-workers/0000018f-a973-df13-a3af-bd77230c0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯数月来首次从拉法向以色列中部特拉维夫发射火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fires-rocket-barrage-from-rafah-at-tel-aviv-central-israel-for-first-time-in-months/0000018f-b4bb-d24f-a5df-feff56040000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，弹幕是从拉法发射的，哈马斯很快承认对火箭弹负责。以色列中部城市多枚火箭弹碎片落下，荷兹利亚一户住宅的屋顶被落下的火箭弹片损坏</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 13:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fires-rocket-barrage-from-rafah-at-tel-aviv-central-israel-for-first-time-in-months/0000018f-b4bb-d24f-a5df-feff56040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电影制片人用原始镜头与 10 月 7 日否认者作斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-film-producer-fighting-october-7-deniers/0000018f-a5d9-d1e2-a1ff-afff06390000</link><description>在制作了两部关于哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的纪录片之后，制作公司首席执行官梅尼·阿维拉姆 (Meny Aviram) 表示，他意识到必须立即讲述这个故事，并为未来保留更多纪录片</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-film-producer-fighting-october-7-deniers/0000018f-a5d9-d1e2-a1ff-afff06390000</guid></item><item><title>喜剧演员戴夫·查佩尔在阿联酋节目中表示以色列正在实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/dave-chappele-says-reasonable-things-but-we-have-to-report-on-them-because-he-said-israel/0000018f-b426-d8a2-a3cf-b4a75fca0000</link><description>在阿布扎比的一场单口喜剧表演中，美国喜剧演员戴夫·查佩尔 (Dave Chappelle) 因评论加沙战争而遭到欢呼和嘲笑，他表示“10 月 7 日发生的事情是不对的”，但“你不应该接受数十次”。我国投入数十亿资金去杀害无辜妇女和儿童</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 10:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/dave-chappele-says-reasonable-things-but-we-have-to-report-on-them-because-he-said-israel/0000018f-b426-d8a2-a3cf-b4a75fca0000</guid></item><item><title>海牙关于以色列的决定具有历史意义，但其意义取决于执行情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hague-decision-on-israel-is-historic-but-its-significance-depends-on-implementation/0000018f-b3de-dfc6-a3ef-b7de2d930000</link><description>这是国际法院首次直接要求以色列停止对巴勒斯坦人的军事行动，但如果美国阻止，裁决将成为一纸空文；代价可能是几代人的更多流血以及全球对国际法信任的削弱</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 09:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hague-decision-on-israel-is-historic-but-its-significance-depends-on-implementation/0000018f-b3de-dfc6-a3ef-b7de2d930000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院对加沙作出裁决后，以色列准备打“外交消耗战”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-diplomatic-war-of-attrition-following-icj-ruling-on-gaza/0000018f-b3b7-dfc6-a3ef-b7ffb5e70000</link><description>在国际法院裁定以色列必须停止在拉法对巴勒斯坦人“造成可能造成物质毁灭的条件”的所有行动后，以色列很快声称“毁灭”过去不是、现在也不是他们的目标。以色列现在将针对其糟糕的公关、联合国和法院发动三线战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 08:32:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-diplomatic-war-of-attrition-following-icj-ruling-on-gaza/0000018f-b3b7-dfc6-a3ef-b7ffb5e70000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加哈南·亚布隆卡（Hanan Yablonka）的葬礼游行，其尸体从加沙找到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-live/idf-denies-hamas-claim-it-captured-israeli-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018f-b2cd-d390-ab8f-f3cdd0fb0000</link><description>救援部门表示，以色列中部地区有两人在火箭弹袭击后受轻伤。 据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，停火和人质释放谈判将于周二恢复。 以色列国防军否认哈马斯在加沙俘获以色列士兵的说法。加沙病毒视频 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了黎巴嫩南部五个村庄的真主党目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-live/idf-denies-hamas-claim-it-captured-israeli-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018f-b2cd-d390-ab8f-f3cdd0fb0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的保镖称，即使在事故发生后，他仍命令司机违反交通法规</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-bodyguards-say-he-orders-drivers-to-violate-traffic-laws-even-after-accident/0000018f-b269-d1e2-a1ff-be6fbd190000</link><description>保镖告诉他们的主管，这种驾驶方式危及他们、本-格维尔部长和路上的任何其他人。上周，对本-格维尔的汽车闯红灯进入十字路口事故的调查结束，警方调查人员认为有足够的证据起诉他的司机</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-bodyguards-say-he-orders-drivers-to-violate-traffic-laws-even-after-accident/0000018f-b269-d1e2-a1ff-be6fbd190000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院的裁决不会立即改变加沙战争，但以色列仍面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/rafah-operation-advances-as-israel-faces-added-pressure-by-icj-ruling-to-end-the-war/0000018f-b179-dfc6-a3ef-b57daa210000</link><description>虽然没有立即采取行动遏制以色列国防军，但从长远来看，存在两个危险：人质危机未得到解决就强行停火，以及错过拜登政府关于美国-沙特-以色列全面协议的提议。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/rafah-operation-advances-as-israel-faces-added-pressure-by-icj-ruling-to-end-the-war/0000018f-b179-dfc6-a3ef-b57daa210000</guid></item><item><title>遵守国际法院的命令是以色列避免成为贱民国家的最后机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/obeying-icj-order-is-israels-last-opportunity-to-save-itself-from-becoming-a-pariah-state/0000018f-b0d0-d8a2-a3cf-b4d34eb40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 21:31:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/obeying-icj-order-is-israels-last-opportunity-to-save-itself-from-becoming-a-pariah-state/0000018f-b0d0-d8a2-a3cf-b4d34eb40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府，呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/thousands-across-israel-protest-netanyahu-government-call-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-b124-d24f-a5df-ffe6cf310000</link><description>人群在全国各地城市集会，加沙被扣押人质的亲属呼吁总理辞职</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 19:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/thousands-across-israel-protest-netanyahu-government-call-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-b124-d24f-a5df-ffe6cf310000</guid></item><item><title>伯利恒附近的巴勒斯坦人如何被驱逐出他们的土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/distance-requirements-and-barriers-how-palestinians-are-being-expelled-from-their-land/0000018f-acf8-df13-a3af-bcfea1270000</link><description>约旦河西岸以色列定居点的距离要求和障碍网络导致巴勒斯坦农民在伯利恒以西的土地上耕种了七个多月</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 18:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/distance-requirements-and-barriers-how-palestinians-are-being-expelled-from-their-land/0000018f-acf8-df13-a3af-bcfea1270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长将调查针对交通部长的腐败指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-to-look-into-corruption-allegations-against-transportation-minister/0000018f-b03a-d8a2-a3cf-b4bbbb2f0000</link><description>一份关于交通部长米里·雷格夫的报告援引了她的前幕僚长的说法，她说她根据地区委员会在利库德集团初选中帮助她的能力来优先考虑当地项目</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 17:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-to-look-into-corruption-allegations-against-transportation-minister/0000018f-b03a-d8a2-a3cf-b4bbbb2f0000</guid></item><item><title>预计数万人将在东耶路撒冷的谢赫贾拉庆祝犹太节日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-expected-to-celebrate-jewish-holiday-in-east-jerusalems-sheik-jarrah/0000018f-b0a6-df13-a3af-b4b681bb0000</link><description>Lag Ba&amp;#39;omer 庆祝活动被禁止在梅隆山举行，活动已转移到东耶路撒冷谢赫贾拉的西蒙·哈扎迪克 (Shimon Hatzaddik) 坟墓举行，该墓在过去几年一直是犹太人和穆斯林之间关系紧张的地区</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 17:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-expected-to-celebrate-jewish-holiday-in-east-jerusalems-sheik-jarrah/0000018f-b0a6-df13-a3af-b4b681bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 232 天：以色列和哈马斯重启停火、人质协议谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-232-israel-and-hamas-to-restart-talks-for-a-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018f-b088-d24f-a5df-feeed2f70000</link><description>埃及和美国同意暂时通过凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点提供援助 ■ 警方调查视频，如果以色列将加沙交给哈马斯和法塔赫，则呼吁不服从 ■ 叙利亚报道：以色列无人机杀死了两名真主党成员；汽车炸弹炸死叙利亚军官 ■ 向以色列驻布鲁塞尔大使馆发射气枪手榴弹 ■ 战争进入 231 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 17:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-232-israel-and-hamas-to-restart-talks-for-a-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018f-b088-d24f-a5df-feeed2f70000</guid></item></channel></rss>